## Limitations

The findings are based on secondary sources, which may not provide a comprehensive view of Ben & Jerry's internal practices and policies. Additionally, the sources primarily reflect opinions and analyses rather than empirical data. Further research, including direct statements from Ben & Jerry's and independent environmental assessments, would provide a more robust understanding of the issue.